summary: A simple player home located near the crossroads between Whiterun, Winterhold and Dawnstar.
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://static.skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/images/36828-1-1372633528.jpg[/img]

[size=4][color=orange]Crossroads Cabin[/color] is a basic starter home I decided to create for myself and now share with everyone else!

This is not an uber-home with alll the bells and whistles in it already.

As most player homes are placed on the outskirts of Whiterun or Riverwood I decided to put this one in a new location. It is located pretty central between Whiterun, Winterhold and Dawnstar (I suppose you could say it\'s a little more Stormcloak oriented based on where it is).

Any bugs or tips you\'d care to share would be greatly appreciated! If you like it, please endorse it![/size]
